    E --> F[Auto-Fix Batch]
    E --> G[Template Generation Batch]
    E --> H[Manual Task Batch]

    F --> I[Batch Verification]
    G --> I

    I --> J{All Verifications Passed?}
    J -->|Yes| K[Commit All Changes]
    J -->|No| L[Partial Rollback]

    K --> M[Progress Report Generation]
    L --> N[Error Analysis & Retry]
```

