---

##  **Data Flow Specifications**

### Primary Workflow: Review to Implementation

```mermaid
graph TD
    A["/review command executed"] --> B[Review Parser]
    B --> C[Recommendation Classifier]
    C --> D{Classification Result}

    D -->|Auto-fixable| E[Auto-Fix Engine]
    D -->|Template-driven| F[Template Generator]
    D -->|Manual| G[Manual Task Creation]

    E --> H[Verification Engine]
    F --> I[Template Processing]
    I --> J[Variable Substitution]
    J --> H

    H --> K{Verification Passed?}
    K -->|Yes| L[Progress Tracker Update]
    K -->|No| M[Rollback/Retry Logic]
    M --> N[Error Reporting]

    L --> O[Implementation Complete]
    G --> P[Manual Task Queue]
```

### Secondary Workflow: Batch Processing

```mermaid
graph TD
    A[Multiple Reviews Input] --> B[Batch Processor]
    B --> C[Dependency Analysis]
    C --> D[Implementation Ordering]
    D --> E[Parallel Processing]

    E --> F[Auto-Fix Batch]
    E --> G[Template Generation Batch]
    E --> H[Manual Task Batch]

    F --> I[Batch Verification]
    G --> I

    I --> J{All Verifications Passed?}
    J -->|Yes| K[Commit All Changes]
    J -->|No| L[Partial Rollback]

    K --> M[Progress Report Generation]
    L --> N[Error Analysis & Retry]
```

### Integration Workflow: Hook System Integration

```mermaid
graph TD
    A[PostToolUse Hook] --> B{Tool Type?}
    B -->|/review| C[RDIS Trigger]
    B -->|Other| D[Standard Processing]

    C --> E[Review Parser Activation]
    E --> F[Classification & Processing]
    F --> G[Implementation Execution]

