# RDIS Technical Specifications

> **Detailed technical specifications for Review-Driven Implementation System components**

---

##  **Component Technical Specifications**

### Review Parser Component

#### Technical Architecture
```typescript
class ReviewParser {
  private readonly patterns: ParsePatterns;
  private readonly validators: ValidationRules;
